tps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Shane-McGowans-funeral-Footage-by-Charles-McQuillan_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Shane-McGowans-funeral-Footage-by-Charles-McQuillan_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Shane-McGowans-funeral-Footage-by-Charles-McQuillan_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Shane-McGowans-funeral-Footage-by-Charles-McQuillan_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Shane-McGowans-funeral-Footage-by-Charles-McQuillan_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>今天（12 月 8 日），粉丝们聚集在都柏林街头，参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shane-macgowan">肖恩·麦高恩 (Shane MacGowan) 的</a>葬礼。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/shane-macgowan-obituary-the-pogues-3551303"><b>Shane MacGowan，1957-2023：一位不妥协、混乱的人</b></a><b> </b></strong></li></ul><p>这位爱尔兰创作型歌手、前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-pogues">Pogues</a>主唱于 11 月 30 日<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shane-macgowans-cause-of-death-revealed-as-wife-honours-the-blessings-he-brought-3553680">因肺炎在医院去世</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-pogues-shane-macgowan-has-died-aged-65-3551301">享年 65 岁</a>。此前，他被诊断出患有脑炎并且健康状况不佳。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-northern-ireland-67636467" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC</em></a>报道，游行活动于格林威治标准时间上午 11 点至 11 点 45 分之间在南部内城周围举行，靠近麦高恩在 Ballsbridge 的居住地。它涉及一辆马车，由阿塔内乐队和一名风笛手领导。</p><p>街道两旁的歌迷们唱着歌曲纪念麦高恩，其中包括《肮脏的老城》和《纽约童话》。</p><p>预计稍后还将有数百人聚集在蒂珀雷里郡尼纳参加麦高恩的葬礼。仪式将于下午 3 点 30 分在尼纳的圣玛丽玫瑰教堂举行，MacGowan 曾在那里参加镇上的弥撒。</p><p>您可以在此处查看游行的镜头和图像： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Pogues 歌手 Shane MacGowan 的葬礼游行" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zbU8CmgEQ08?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><figure id="attachment_3556202" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3556202" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3556202" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Shane-MacGowans-funeral-procession-Footage-by-Charles-McQuillan_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="肖恩·麦克高恩" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Shane-MacGowans-funeral-procession-Footage-by-Charles-McQuillan_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Shane-MacGowans-funeral-procession-Footage-by-Charles-McQuillan_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Shane-MacGowans-funeral-procession-Footage-by-Charles-McQuillan_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Shane-MacGowans-funeral-procession-Footage-by-Charles-McQuillan_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Shane-MacGowans-funeral-procession-Footage-by-Charles-McQuillan_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Shane-MacGowans-funeral-procession-Footage-by-Charles-McQuillan_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3556202" class="wp-caption-text">肖恩·麦高恩的送葬队伍——查尔斯·麦克奎伦拍摄的镜头_盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3556204" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3556204" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3556204" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Shane-MacBowan-Photo-by-Liam-McBurney_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="肖恩·麦克高恩" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Shane-MacBowan-Photo-by-Liam-McBurney_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Shane-MacBowan-